        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/30234",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ibschreiber",
                        "name": "ibschreiber",
                        "displayName": "Michael Schreiber",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Hello,\nfirst comment here, let's see :)\n\nI had the same problem, trying to change the property didn't probagate to the renderer. \nThis is how i did it:\n\n{code:title=bootstrap.php}\n...\n$viewRenderer = Zend_Controller_Action_HelperBroker::getStaticHelper('viewRenderer');\n$viewRenderer->setViewSuffix('php');\nunset($viewRenderer);\n...\n{code}\n\nif necessary one can change the suffix in the Controllers by using \n{code}\n$this->_helper->viewRenderer->setViewSuffix('php');\n{code}\n\nHave fun!",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ibschreiber",
                        "name": "ibschreiber",
                        "displayName": "Michael Schreiber",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-04-17T11:08:41.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-04-17T11:08:41.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/39534",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=anselm",
                        "name": "anselm",
                        "displayName": "Anselm F\u00f6hr",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Still present in 1.9.7. Is think this should be fixed.\r\n\r\nBut so long, thanks for the workaround, Michael.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=anselm",
                        "name": "anselm",
                        "displayName": "Anselm F\u00f6hr",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-03-25T08:13:44.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-03-25T08:13:44.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/42389",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ryan.lange",
                        "name": "ryan.lange",
                        "displayName": "Ryan Lange",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Reed Underwood wrote:\r\n> \"It looks to me like $viewSuffix was intended to propagate to the viewRenderer helper in Zend_Controller_Action.\"\r\n\r\nThat was my impression, too, but apparently it's the other way around...\r\n\r\n{code:title=Zend\/Controller\/Action\/Helper\/ViewRenderer.php (ZF 1.10.8)}\r\n498:        \/\/ Register view with action controller (unless already registered)\r\n499:        if ((null !== $this->_actionController) && (null === $this->_actionController->view)) {\r\n500:            $this->_actionController->view       = $this->view;\r\n501:            $this->_actionController->viewSuffix = $this->_viewSuffix;\r\n502:        }\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nLine #501 explicitly sets the action controller's $viewSuffix property to that of the ViewRenderer's $_viewSuffix property. So any change to the $viewSuffix property within the controller gets overwritten by the ViewRenderer.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ryan.lange",
                        "name": "ryan.lange",
                        "displayName": "Ryan Lange",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-09-29T07:14:51.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-09-29T07:14:51.000+0000"
                }
            ]
        }
    },
